==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exhaustive
<hw>Ex*haust"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Serving or
tending to exhaust; exhibiting all the facts or arguments; <as>as, an
<ex>exhaustive method</ex></as>.</def>
<wordforms><wf>Ex*haust"ive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exhaustless</ent>⟦br⟧
